project PhoneE164

task ValidateE164Number
    goal
        Return True iff a string is a valid E.164 phone number.
    input
        s
    output
        is_valid
    constraint
        Function name is is_valid_e164.
        Module is impl.py.
        Return type is bool.
        Format is a plus sign followed by 1 to 15 digits.
        The first digit after the plus must not be 0.
    test
        A common 11-digit US number returns True.
        A 12-digit UK number returns True.
        A 15-digit number (the max) returns True.
        A 16-digit number is rejected.
        Missing plus prefix returns False.
        Bare plus with nothing after returns False.
        Empty string returns False.
        Plus followed by a leading zero returns False.
        Non-digit characters after the plus return False.
        Non-string input raises TypeError.
    success
        Every acceptance case above matches exactly.
